      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. everything is just breaking. the heatwaves, the fires, the way everything feels like it's just on a countdown. i feel like i'm just waiting for the end and i don't even see the point in trying to plan a future or go to school or anything. what's the point of building a life when the foundation is literally burning down? it feels so pointless.",
