      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is a profound and necessary realization that the world is changing rapidly, and it is completely valid to feel that your personal struggles are insignificant against such a backdrop. However, the most honest path forward is to acknowledge this reality without letting it dictate your entire existence, choosing instead to find meaning in the small, immediate moments that still exist. You do not have to build a grand future to validate your life today; simply being present and observing the world, even in its imperfection, is an act of courage that defies the idea that we must fight for a dying future.",
