    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread and a desire to stop participating in life due to global crises and climate change. The assistant responds by validating the user's perspective on the state of the world but ultimately directs the user toward finding meaning in small moments and maintaining presence, rather than encouraging self-harm.",
